'''加布里埃尔·贝隆·丰塞卡·德索萨'''（{{lang-pt|Gabriel Veron Fonseca de Souza}}；{{bd|2002年|9月3日}}），简称“'''加布里埃尔·贝隆'''”（{{lang-pt|Gabriel Veron}}），是一名巴西足球运动员，场上司职[[前锋_(足球)|前锋]]，目前效力于[[巴西足球甲级联赛|巴甲]]球队[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]。

==俱乐部生涯==
贝隆出生在[[巴西|巴西]][[北里奥格兰德州|北里奥格兰德州]]的[[阿苏|阿苏]]，他在2017年从家乡球队{{le|纳塔尔圣克鲁斯足球俱乐部|Santa Cruz Futebol Clube (RN)|纳塔尔圣克鲁斯}}加入了[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]青训。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.op9.com.br/blogs/blog-do-marcos-lopes/gabriel-veron-do-santa-cruz-de-natal-para-o-melhor-jogador-do-mundial-sub-17/|title=Gabriel Veron, o melhor do Mundial Sub-17, saiu do Santa Cruz de Natal|trans-title=Gabriel Veron, the best of the under-17 World Cup, came out of Santa Cruz de Natal|publisher=Sistema Opinião|language=pt-BR|date=2019-11-18|access-date=2019-11-29}}{{Dead link}}</ref>2018年6月，贝隆帮助[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]U-17夺得了在马德里自治区举办的U-17[[国际足联俱乐部世界杯|世俱杯]]冠军，这也是他们的首座国际奖杯。贝隆个人也获得了赛事金靴奖以及赛事最佳球员的称号。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://palmeiras.com.br/news/2018/06/06/melhor-do-mundial-sub-17--gabriel-veron-celebra-titulo-pelo-verdao---fizemos-historia-.shtml|title=Melhor do Mundial Sub-17, Gabriel Veron celebra título pelo Verdão: ‘Fizemos história’|trans-title=Best of the under-17 World Cup, Gabriel Veron celebrates title with ''Verdão'': 'We made history'|publisher=SE Palmeiras|language=pt-BR|date=2018-06-06|access-date=2019-11-29}}{{Dead link}}</ref>

2018年11月14日，贝隆与[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]签下了他的第一份职业合同，为期3年，至2021年。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.basepalmeiras.com.br/2018/11/14/gabriel-veron-assina-seu-primeiro-contrato-profissional-com-palmeiras/|title=Gabriel Veron assina seu primeiro contrato profissional com Palmeiras|trans-title=Gabriel Veron signs his first professional contract with Palmeiras|publisher=Base Palmeiras|language=pt-BR|date=2018-11-14|access-date=2019-11-29|archive-date=2020-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926062722/https://basepalmeiras.com.br/2018/11/14/gabriel-veron-assina-seu-primeiro-contrato-profissional-com-palmeiras/}}</ref>差不多一年后，在他从国家队比赛归来后，贝隆同意与[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]续约3年。这份合同将会在他的18岁生日当天生效。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/palmeiras/noticia/palmeiras-faz-acordo-para-renovar-o-contrato-de-gabriel-veron-destaque-do-mundial-sub-17.ghtml|title=Palmeiras renova o contrato de Gabriel Veron, destaque do Mundial Sub-17; veja os detalhes|trans-title=Palmeiras renew contract of Gabriel Veron, spotlight of the U17 World CUp; see details|publisher=Globo Esporte|language=pt-BR|date=2019-11-21|access-date=2019-11-29|archive-date=2021-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210324223857/https://globoesporte.globo.com/futebol/times/palmeiras/noticia/palmeiras-faz-acordo-para-renovar-o-contrato-de-gabriel-veron-destaque-do-mundial-sub-17.ghtml}}</ref>

2019年11月28日，在[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]0-1惜败[[弗鲁米嫩塞足球俱乐部|弗鲁米嫩塞]]的[[巴西足球甲级联赛|巴甲]]比赛中，贝隆于下半场替补上阵，换下了{{le|威廉 (1986年生足球运动员)|Willian (footballer, born 1986)|威廉}}，完成了一线队以及[[巴西足球甲级联赛|巴甲]]首秀。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.terra.com.br/esportes/lance/gabriel-veron-admite-frio-na-barriga-em-estreia-no-profissional,d5afd754a919593fea1d2c0e704a21671bd2aezd.html|title=Gabriel Veron admite frio na barriga em estreia no profissional|trans-title=Gabriel Veron admits butterflies in the stomach in his professional debut|publisher=Terra|language=pt-BR|date=2019-11-28|access-date=2019-11-29|archive-date=2020-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200723210501/https://www.terra.com.br/esportes/lance/gabriel-veron-admite-frio-na-barriga-em-estreia-no-profissional,d5afd754a919593fea1d2c0e704a21671bd2aezd.html}}</ref>同年12月5日，在[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]5-1完胜[[戈亚斯体育俱乐部|戈亚斯]]的[[巴西足球甲级联赛|巴甲]]比赛中，贝隆于下半场替补登场，打进两球并为{{le|杜杜 (1992年生足球运动员)|Dudu (footballer, born 1992)|杜杜}}送出了一记助攻。这两粒进球也使他成为了[[帕尔梅拉斯体育俱乐部|帕尔梅拉斯]]队史上进球第二年轻的球员。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.esporteinterativo.com.br/brasileirao/Gabriel-Veron-brilha-em-goleada-e-alcana-marca-historica-no-Palmeiras-20191205-0033.html|title=Gabriel Veron brilha em goleada e alcança marca histórica no Palmeiras|trans-title=Gabriel Veron shines in routing and reaches historic mark at Palmeiras|publisher=Esporte Interativo|language=pt-BR|date=2019-12-05|access-date=2019-12-06|archive-date=2020-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020164209/https://www.esporteinterativo.com.br/brasileirao/Gabriel-Veron-brilha-em-goleada-e-alcana-marca-historica-no-Palmeiras-20191205-0033.html}}</ref>贝隆同样也是在[[南美解放者杯|南美解放者杯]]中进球最年轻的球员。

==国家队生涯==
2019年9月20日，贝隆以主力的身份入选了[[巴西17岁以下国家足球队|巴西U-17]]主教练吉列尔梅·达拉·德阿的[[2019年国际足联U-17世界杯|2019年U-17世界杯]]的21人大名单。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.cbf.com.br/selecao-brasileira/noticias/copa-mundo-sub17/selecao-brasileira-sub-17-convocados-para-a-copa-do-mundo-no-brasil|title=Seleção Brasileira Sub-17: convocados para a Copa do Mundo no Brasil|trans-title=Brazil under-17 team: called up for the World Cup in Brazil|publisher=CBF|language=pt-BR|date=2019-09-20|access-date=2019-11-29|archive-date=2020-10-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201029152707/https://www.cbf.com.br/selecao-brasileira/noticias/copa-mundo-sub17/selecao-brasileira-sub-17-convocados-para-a-copa-do-mundo-no-brasil}}</ref>在[[巴西17岁以下国家足球队|巴西U-17]]夺得他们的第4座[[国际足联U-17世界杯|U-17世界杯]]的征程中，贝隆作为无可争议的主力贡献了3粒进球，<ref name="FIFA">{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/u17worldcup/news/brazil-defeat-mexico-to-take-top-prize-at-fifa-u-17-world-cup|title=Last-gasp Brazil edge Mexico to be crowned U-17 kings|publisher=FIFA.com|date=2019-11-17|access-date=2019-11-29|archive-date=2021-08-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210808235217/https://www.fifa.com/tournaments/mens/u17worldcup/brazil2019/news/brazil-defeat-mexico-to-take-top-prize-at-fifa-u-17-world-cup}}</ref>并获得了赛事金球奖。<ref name="FIFA2">{{cite web|url=https://www.fifa.com/u17worldcup/news/brazilians-headline-the-award-winners-3057636|title=Brazilians headline list of award winners|publisher=FIFA.com|date=2019-11-17|access-date=2019-11-21|archive-date=2021-02-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210228131046/https://www.fifa.com/u17worldcup/news/brazilians-headline-the-award-winners-3057636}}</ref>

